      <title>Markdown语法</title>
      <link href="2020/08/21/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>2020/08/21/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语言，能将文本换成有效的XHTML(或者HTML)文档，它的目标是实现易读易写，成为一种适用于网络的书写语言。本文主要讲述Markdown 基本语法。</p><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><p>要创建标题，请在单词或短语前面添加井号 (<code>#</code>) 。井号的数量代表了标题的级别。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><p><img src="//p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/3568665c5b7148d48ef722db8b5b7f13~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image" alt="博客标题"></p><h2 id="粗体"><a href="#粗体" class="headerlink" title="粗体"></a>粗体</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>渲染效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code> **粗体**</code></td><td><strong>粗体</strong></td></tr><tr><td><code> __粗体__</code></td><td><strong>粗体</strong></td></tr><tr><td><code>我是**粗体**字</code></td><td>我是<strong>粗体</strong>字</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="斜体"><a href="#斜体" class="headerlink" title="斜体"></a>斜体</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>渲染效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code> *粗体*</code></td><td><em>粗体</em></td></tr><tr><td><code> _斜体_</code></td><td><em>粗体</em></td></tr><tr><td><code>我是*斜体*字</code></td><td>我是<em>粗体</em>字</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="粗斜体"><a href="#粗斜体" class="headerlink" title="粗斜体"></a>粗斜体</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>渲染效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code> ***粗斜体***</code></td><td><strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong></td></tr><tr><td><code> ___粗斜体___</code></td><td><strong><em>粗斜体</em></strong></td></tr><tr><td><code>我是***粗斜体***字</code></td><td>我是**<em>粗斜体**</em>字</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="块引用"><a href="#块引用" class="headerlink" title="块引用"></a>块引用</h2><p>要创建块引用，请在段落前添加一个 <code>&gt;</code> 符号。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 块引用示例</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下所示：</p><blockquote><p>块引用示例</p></blockquote><h2 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h2><p>要创建有序列表，请在每个列表项前添加数字并紧跟一个英文句点。数字不必按数学顺序排列，但是列表应当以数字 1 起始。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 表项1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 表项2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 表项3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    1.</span> 表项(1)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    2.</span> 表项(2)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">4.</span> 表项4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><ol><li>表项1</li><li>表项2</li><li>表项3<ol><li>表项(1)</li><li>表项(2)</li></ol></li><li>表项4</li></ol><h2 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h2><p>要创建无序列表，请在每个列表项前面添加破折号 (<code>-</code>)、星号 (<code>*</code>) 或加号 (<code>+</code>) 。缩进一个或多个列表项可创建嵌套列表。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 内表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 内表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 表项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><ul><li>表项</li><li>表项</li><li>表项<ul><li>内表项</li><li>内表项</li></ul></li><li>表项</li></ul><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>要将单词或短语表示为代码，请将其包裹在反引号 (```) 中。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">开始讲<span class="code">`printf()`</span> 函数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><p>开始讲<code>printf()</code> 函数</p><h2 id="代码块"><a href="#代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码块"></a>代码块</h2><p>要创建代码块，请将代码块的每一行缩进至少四个空格或一个制表符。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">system(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello world!\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">system(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分隔线"><a href="#分隔线" class="headerlink" title="分隔线"></a>分隔线</h2><p>要创建分隔线，请在单独一行上使用三个或多个星号 (<code>***</code>)、破折号 (<code>---</code>) 或下划线 (<code>___</code>) ，并且不能包含其他内容。为了兼容性，请在分隔线的前后均添加空白行。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis">---</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span>_</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上三个分隔线的渲染效果看起来都一样：</p><hr><hr><hr><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">朋友的博客</span>](<span class="link">https://n0usec.top/</span>)</span><br><span class="line">添加提示信息：</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">朋友的博客</span>](<span class="link">https://n0usec.top/ &quot;NOus&#x27;s Blog&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：<br><a href="https://n0usec.top/">朋友的博客</a><br>添加提示信息：<br><a href="https://n0usec.top/" title="NOus&#39;s Blog">朋友的博客</a></p><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">颜色</span>](<span class="link">//p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/27b89daa44274b7ebd5005c836d22c81~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image</span>)</span><br><span class="line">添加提示信息：</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">颜色</span>](<span class="link">//p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/82b5fafec1d745ef96edaa4e818ffd90~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image &quot;颜色&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><p><img src="//p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/155fe3d4db8743a4859f711addd9a555~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image" alt="颜色"><br>添加提示信息(即图片名)：<br><img src="//p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/658bad386c784a49961f1a7913971f87~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-1.image" alt="颜色" title="颜色"></p><h2 id="转义字符"><a href="#转义字符" class="headerlink" title="转义字符"></a>转义字符</h2><p>要显示原本用于格式化 Markdown 文档的字符，请在字符前面添加反斜杠字符 (<code>\</code>) 。</p><h2 id="善用-HTML"><a href="#善用-HTML" class="headerlink" title="善用 HTML"></a>善用 HTML</h2><p>我们可以在 Markdown 中插入一些简单的 HTML 代码或 CSS 片段来获得更多扩展，使得文章内容更具有多样性。以下演示几个简单功能。</p><h3 id="文字颜色"><a href="#文字颜色" class="headerlink" title="文字颜色"></a>文字颜色</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>  <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;color: #519D9E; &quot;</span>&gt;</span>#519D9E颜色演示<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：<span  style="color: #519D9E; ">#519D9E颜色演示</span></p><h3 id="文字大小"><a href="#文字大小" class="headerlink" title="文字大小"></a>文字大小</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>  <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;font-size:0.7em;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>0.7em 文字大小演示<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：<span  style="font-size:0.7em;">0.7em 文字大小演示</span></p><h3 id="文字位置"><a href="#文字位置" class="headerlink" title="文字位置"></a>文字位置</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text-align:center&quot;</span>&gt;</span>内容居中演示<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"># 可以修改 text-align 参数来设置文字位置。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>渲染效果如下：</p><p style="text-align:center">内容居中演示</p> <h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><ol><li><a href="https://www.markdown.xyz/">Markdown 指南中文版</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs">Hexo Fluid 用户手册</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
